            <title>[LU-3746] Test failure on test suite lustre-rsync-test, subtest test_1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3746</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for girish &amp;lt;gshilamkar@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82b98a06-0152-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82b98a06-0152-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_1 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;/tmp/target/d0.lustre-rsync-test/d1/file5: user.foo: No such attribute&lt;br/&gt;
/tmp/target2/d0.lustre-rsync-test/d1/file5: user.foo: No such attribute&lt;br/&gt;
 lustre-rsync-test test_1: @@@@@@ FAIL: Error in replicating xattrs. &lt;br/&gt;
  Trace dump:&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4202:error_noexit()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4229:error()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/lustre-rsync-test.sh:196:test_1()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4483:run_one()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4516:run_one_logged()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4371:run_test()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/lustre-rsync-test.sh:208:main()&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: lustre-rsync-test 1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
